data.description: ***This home qualifies for a $5000 grant from Chase.*** Welcome home to this nicely maintained home in the GUARDED golf community of Briggs Ranch. This home has the perfect combination of privacy and quiet elegance that you would expect from Bellaire Homes. Backing to a greenbelt, you can enjoy the stars while sitting out on the deck or by the firepit with friends in the backyard. An additional feature is that your kids will attend top rated Medina Valley ISD schools. Inside, enjoy the maintenance free oversized tile flooring in all the open spaces and wet areas. The open floorplan is the perfect setup if you like to entertain, as allows free, easy movement between the kitchen, living room and dining room. The study provides a clearly defined workspace, separating work life from home life. With too many features to list, this home is a must see! Set up your showing today!
